dct_title_s: New-York city & county map : with vicinity entire, Brooklyn, Williamsburgh, Jersey City &c. in the 79th year of the independence of the United States
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Hand colored. Map within decorative border. Includes ill., key, and insets of Declaration of Independence within illustrative border and map of Long Island. Also shows names of adjacent landowners, positions of old roads and buildings and the original shoreline. Includes "Conveyances." Oriented with north to the upper left. Historic Maps copy has "c" added in ms. to "Dykeman's" in title. Cadastral map.
dct_publisher_sm: [New York : City Surveyor, 187-?] (N[ew] Y[ork] : Mayer, Merkel & Ottmann, lith.)
